Revision history for Devel-MAT-Tool-Future

0.03    2023-10-26
        [CHANGES]
         * Module style updates:
            + Swap unit tests from `Test::More` to `Test2::V0`
         * Better reliability when detecting PP vs XS-based futures

        [BUGFIXES]
         * Account for `magic ~` output when testing the `show` command

0.02    2022-10-03
        [CHANGES]
         * Updates to handle both Future::PP and Future::XS

0.01    2022-08-30
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
